The paper deals with computer vision techniques to monitor cassava diseases, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The use of semi-supervised approaches also suggests a possible connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions the use of annotations, which could involve natural language processing (cs.CL) techniques. Finally, the mention of disease severity could suggest a connection to computer security and cryptography (cs.CR) sub-category.
